   spatial patterns that encourage foraging behavior.

3. **Inspector Panel**: Real-time agent monitoring with selection, focus, and
   detailed sensor/output display. The snapshot-based architecture prevents
   UI locking while maintaining high-fidelity debugging capabilities.

